{"tid":1451283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都話未係時機？時機就係一觸即發！已經有好充分理由無限罷工！","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:19:07.000Z","uid":300554,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8686ba1fdc4f8415b038ee29f32bb218afe56ded","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"一米開槍，一觸即發！我哋用行動做文宣，一路罷一路叫人罷，全民因情緒病告假！<br />\n上次八五二百班機取消，林鄭驚到賴尿，今次要佢全面起唔到機！<br />\n我哋要主動奪回自主權，從來沒有廉價抗爭，Freedom is not free！We can&rsquo;t sit on our hands and claim we&rsquo;ve done all we can all along.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJiOdcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJiOdcw.jpg&h=86d4e818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mD92hvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmD92hvY.jpg&h=e1cb58e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SGstCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SGstCD.jpg&h=dc791769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuxfCvZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuxfCvZ.jpg&h=5411f5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eh3ZjKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feh3ZjKj.jpg&h=2bbf88eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LjPd8CE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjPd8CE.jpg&h=2b6ee04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bnLfhE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bnLfhE.jpg&h=ce65bf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLp2hxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLp2hxR.jpg&h=d53e75d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY0MKcR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F