/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"你今日上唔到機<br />\n是為了他日有個自由港俾你安全起機"},{"pid":"ee1dc6c391bd375d992412af377030ff560252ac","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">暴權，正向我們身心施以殘害。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">返工，不能填補基本身心需要。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">罷工，是發自良心，基於人權！</span>"},{"pid":"97f66bbaf2d16ddc0edfc746b93f04d33b4f3e73","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:07:05.000Z","msg":"【九月罷課 學生自決】<br />\n<br />\n六七八月，香港風起，然今煙淚未散而存。過去，中學生發起學生聯署反對送中惡法，甚至以身把淚血拼煙雲，仍是未能得到合理之回應。暑假已臨暮昏，惜送中惡法危機仍存，警、政、民關係更是未嘗得治。開學之日即將上演，我等中學生不能坐以待斃，必須繼續堅持心中的理想，無計可施下，以罷課凝聚中學生力量，讓政府明白，我等非枉讀之輩，稍懂筆墨亦同存良心，敢於環看政治。<br />\n<br />\n雖未讀盡萬卷書，但我等亦願走萬里路，為香港，萬里路比起萬卷書，何重何輕？<br />\n<br />\n故就罷課事宜，香港各大中學生組織包括中學時政、青年前線、悉政學揚、學生動源及學生抗爭力量將成立聯盟，名曰香港學生罷課聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n望能因此喚醒中學生對政治觸覺，讓中學生行使公民責任，勇於發聲，向政府證明中學生力量。同時提升中學生對反修例運動參與度。<br />\n<br />\n蔽盟歡迎各學生組織加入聯盟，僅此望各界支援學生大罷課！<br />\n<br />\n鈞鑒<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟創始組織<br />\n中學時政<br />\n青年前線<br />\n悉政學揚<br />\n學生動源<br />\n學生抗爭力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月10日<br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Facebook Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongStudentStrikeAlliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongStudentStrikeAlliance&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=2b190e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongStudentStrikeAlliance</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Instagram Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/studentstrikesept?igshid=14lh92elzufd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstudentstrikesept%3Figshid%3D14lh92elzufd0&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f4d9eed6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/studentstrikesept?igshid=14lh92elzufd0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Telegram Channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkongstudentstrikealliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongstudentstrikealliance&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=1f26abae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkongstudentstrikealliance</a>"},{"pid":"88eb4cbb58f24e85c97b69e1541a2a229b82028d","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"他們昨夜在街頭為爭取你的自由頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n8.12 不罷不休<br />\n<br />\n你今天要踩著地上他們被沖掉的血跡去上班？"},{"pid":"8541b1194cb4b69f79bd594be28dc88b41fc87f4","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:08:36.000Z","msg":"當你要保住的<span style=\"color: red;\">飯碗</span>開始滲血，你可以<span style=\"color: blue;\">無知無覺無感無味</span>？"},{"pid":"622d4b828cf337d3c84f1ff218411c8b368c60af","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:09:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\">這是災難性的時刻<br />\n即是無限罷工開始</span>"},{"pid":"82b6346a094fd532165400ce4f9b407d50ad7216","tid":1451283,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:19:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">打破秩序，是為了重整秩序</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e46664fbd83081f6fb17f925e765dd579c1ba1b9","tid":1451283,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"【幫手推】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19dbd292ac96df8acc9991d046c55dba6b2d55c5","tid":1451283,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:44.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://l